South African Gold Production Fell 3.5% in July From Year Ago, Agency Says

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-09-08T09:30:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/south-african-gold-production-fell-3-5-in-july-from-year-ago-agency-says.html
South African  gold production  fell
3.5 percent in July from a year earlier, Jean-Pierre Terblanche,
a spokesman for Statistics South  Africa , said by phone from
 Pretoria  today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
